for a medical emergency, seek emergency medical assistance immediately by dialing 911 or go to the nearest emergency facility. see list of emergency facilities below. all visits to the sjsu student health center are confidential, as the university complies with the health insurance portability and accountability act (hipaa) and the family educational rights and privacy act (ferpa). medical records are kept confidential and will not be released without written consent. same day appointments are designed to accommodate students who are assessed to require medical attention on the day they call regarding their medical concern. appointments cancelled and/or rescheduled on the same day will be charged a missed appointment fee. advance appointments are scheduled for medical concerns that are not assessed as needing urgent medical attention. need to cancel your appointment? to cancel: appointments must be cancelled before 7:30 a.m. the day of the scheduled appointment, or a missed appointment fee will be charged. phone: 408-924-6122 appointments/general info 408-924-6150 patient billing the student wellness center building (swc) is located across from the event center. parking is available in the seventh street garage. student wellness center san josé state university one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0037 monday - thursday: 8:30 a.m. to 4:30 p.m. friday (march 31): closed monday - thursday: 8:30am – 5:00pm friday: 8:30am – 4:30pm call to schedule an appointment 